ZH: 请通报我这次的会议时间和地点。
EN: Please inform me of the time and location of this meeting.

ZH: 他们选择通过邮件通报最新的公司动态。
EN: They choose to update the latest company news by email.

ZH: 这个部门的每个成员都要通报自己的工作进展。
EN: Every member of this department has to report their work progress.

ZH: 我将会通报这个事件给上级领导。
EN: I will report this incident to the higher authorities.

ZH: 他通过微信群通报了公司的最新决定。
EN: He informed the latest decision of the company through the WeChat group.

ZH: 去接待处通报一下我们的到访。
EN: Go to the reception desk and notify them of our arrival.

ZH: 警察立即通报了这个重要的线索。
EN: The police immediately reported this important clue.

ZH: 我们应该及时通报任何有关的问题和困难。
EN: We should promptly notify any relevant problems and difficulties.

ZH: 这个消息就应该通报给所有员工。
EN: This news should be communicated to all employees.

ZH: 请将这份文件通报给每一个部门负责人。
EN: Please distribute this document to every department head.

ZH: 船长将船只状态通报给港务局。
EN: The captain reported the status of the ship to the port authority.

ZH: 他会定期通报我们的工作进展和成果。
EN: He will regularly report our work progress and achievements.

ZH: 公司需要通报的事项都会在每个月的会议上讨论。
EN: Matters that need to be reported by the company will be discussed in the monthly meeting.

ZH: 政府通过媒体通报了新的法律法规。
EN: The government announced the new laws and regulations through the media.

ZH: 您可以通过网站向我们通报任何问题或建议。
EN: You can report any problems or suggestions to us through the website.

ZH: 社区通报了一起窃贼入室盗窃案。
EN: The community informed about a burglary incident.

ZH: 医院会通报任何疑似传染病病例。
EN: The hospital will report any suspected cases of infectious diseases.

ZH: 记者向公众通报了这个重要的新闻。
EN: The journalist informed the public about this important news.

ZH: 老师会将你的进步通报给你的家长。
EN: The teacher will report your progress to your parents.

ZH: 通报了一项紧急会议，所有员工都必须参加。
EN: A urgent meeting has been notified, and all employees must attend.
